<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>About Us - <%= title %></title> <!-- Dynamic Title -->
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
      color: #333;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    /* Nav Bar */
    .navbar {
      background-color: white;
      padding: 15px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .navbar a {
      color: black;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    .navbar a:hover {
      background-color: #c2c4c5;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }

    /* About Us  */
    .about-us {
      background-color: #fff;
      padding: 50px 20px;
      color: #222;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    h1, h2 {
      color: #2c3e50;
      text-align: center;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 36px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 28px;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 18px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #555;
    }

    ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding-left: 0;
    }

    ul li {
      font-size: 18px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      background-color: #ecf0f1;
      margin: 10px 0;
      padding: 10px;
      border-left: 4px solid #3498db;
    }

    ul li:hover {
      background-color: #d0e8f4;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Nav Bar -->
  <div class="navbar">
    <a href="/"><b>Home</b></a> <!-- Changed link to EJS route -->
    <a href="/about"><b>About Us</b></a> <!-- Changed link to EJS route -->
    <a href="/contact"><b>Contact Us</b></a> <!-- Changed link to EJS route -->
  </div>

  <!-- About Us -->
  <section class="about-us">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>About Us</h1>
      <p>Welcome to <%= appName %>! We're a local classifieds and community platform designed to connect people for buying, selling, and exchanging goods and services. Whether you're looking for a place to stay, items to buy, or want to offer your own services, <%= appName %> provides a trusted space for local transactions.</p>

      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>At <%= appName %>, we believe in fostering strong local connections and promoting sustainable, community-driven commerce. Our platform is built to make buying and selling easier, safer, and more accessible for everyone.</p>

      <h2>What We Offer</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Buy & Sell Locally: Find great deals on items you need or sell your own goods easily.</li>
        <li>Trusted Listings: All our listings are community-driven, allowing for safe exchanges.</li>
        <li>Community Focused: We're more than just a marketplace. We're here to support local businesses and promote neighborhood connections.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>How It Works</h2>
      <p>Simply create a free account, post your ads, browse listings, and connect with others in your community. From finding food to housing, <%= appName %> brings your local market online.</p>

      <h2>Our Values</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Trust</li>
        <li>Community</li>
        <li>Convenience</li>
      </ul>

      <p>Thank you for choosing <%= appName %>â€”where local communities come together!</p>
    </div>
  </section>

</body>
</html>


